//////////////////////////////////////////////
// Backlog ///////////////////////////////////
//////////////////////////////////////////////
* Replace hard-coded strings with XML resources.
* Replace hard-coded colors with XML resources.
* Unit Tests
* Make fragment transactions smooth.
* Ask users to rate the app every once in a while.
* Option for flame-out hops (calculate IBU) (Not enough science for an equation yet).
* Some misc items use volume instead of weight (orange peel, coriander seeds, for example)
* Can search web for BeerXML Recipes
* Can't start brew timer if all grain, no mash steps.
* Calculate water to grain ratio when not auto calculating water to add.
* When entering measured gravity, user can also input temperature.
* Mash temperature graph
* Recipe revisions
* Search recipes
* First time use hints / help.
* Should update mash profiles used in recipes when a profile is edited?
* Support different times for mash ingredients?
* Quick add button when nothing in a list.
* Add Style guide viewing tool.
* Can configure bottle / keg age.
* Equipment Editor?
* Perform mash calculation automatically
* Maybe - Make a visual scale rather than numerical for recipe stats. e.g, FG, OG, Color.
* Modify desired traits and the app will auto-modify your recipe to match?
* Handle actually setting the amount of yeast.
* Should consider mash temp in ABV calc.
* Add support for more custom fields to XML import / export.
* Brewer profiles, social features?  This is a big task.
* Support measured gravities < 1
* Can choose where to export recipes.
* Better integration with Dropbox / Google Drive

